title: NFL Talk, Bobby Brown, Are You Smarter Than Tommy, Tommy VS Junior, Old VS Young, Carla's Reality Update, Power, Closing Remarks and more.
itunes:title: NFL Talk, Bobby Brown, Are You Smarter Than Tommy, Tommy VS Junior, Old VS Young, Carla's Reality Update, Power, Closing Remarks and more.
description:
Today is the first day of NFL action. The crew talk about the Cleveland Browns and Colin Kaepernick. Bobby Brown's story on BET aired part 2 and the ladies talk about it. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Tommy VS Junior. The Strawberry Letter was so unique today that a reenactment was needed. Miss Carla did Reality Update and catching up with Power was the focus. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about valuing ourselves and more.
